aVToday, I, as the mother of a six-year-old,
p15
aVwalk into Barnes and Noble,
p16
aVand see this.
p17
aVAnd it is amazing
p18
aVthe variety that one finds  on those shelves.
p19
aVThere are guides to raising  an eco-friendly kid,
p20
aVa gluten-free kid,
p21
aVa disease-proof kid,
p22
aVwhich, if you ask me, is a little bit creepy.
p23
aVThere are guides to raising a bilingual kid
p24
aVeven if you only speak one language at home.
p25
aVThere are guides to raising a financially savvy kid
p26
aVand a science-minded kid
p27
aVand a kid who is a whiz at yoga.
