aa(lp32
VAll of these books are well-intentioned.
p33
aVI am sure that many of them are great.
p34
aVBut taken together, I am sorry,
p35
aVI do not see help
p36
aVwhen I look at that shelf.
p37
aVI see anxiety.
p38
aVI see a giant candy-colored monument
p39
aVto our collective panic,
p40
aVand it makes me want to know,
p41
aVwhy is it that raising our children
p42
aVis associated with so much anguish
p43
aVand so much confusion?
p44
aVWhy is it that we are at sixes and sevens
p45
aVabout the one thing human beings
p46
aVhave been doing successfully for millennia,
p47
aVlong before parenting message boards
p48
aVand peer-reviewed studies came along?
